    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1907-01-11T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1907-01-11T00:00:00-05:00" n="348"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d348">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 3507.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of State</gloss> to
                        Ambassador <persName type="to">Meyer</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1907-01-11">
                            <hi rend="italic">January 11, 1907</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                    <seg rendition="#left">No. 204.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir</hi>: I have the honor to acknowledge the receipt of
                    your No. 717, of the 15th ultimo, reporting the application of Clemens Belling
                    for a passport.</p>
                <p>From the facts stated he appears to be an American citizen by birth, and the
                    animus revertendi is alleged.</p>
                <pb facs="1126" n="976" xml:id="pg_976"/>
                <p>There seems to be no circumstances which show an establishment in any other
                    country. The nature of his calling, that of a circus performer, is such that his
                    life must be nomadic.</p>
                <p>The department is of opinion that a passport should be granted him.</p>
                <p>I am, etc.,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Robert Bacon.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
